  "2026-07-05T05:51:11.797Z",claude-code-agent,"Progress evidence from child items pm-lodl/pm-8778: SDK-first baseline is now explicit and enforceable. Current private boundary debt is quantified at 857 unique src/core import edges across 91 boundary files (101 scanned) from src/cli.ts, src/cli/**, and src/mcp/**. The static quality gate now prevents growth and stale baseline entries, giving each SDK primitive-promotion lane a measurable ratchet target while preserving the project philosophy 'project management = context management'."
  "2026-07-06T22:31:27.762Z",codex-agent,"Planning evidence 2026-07-06/07 codex-agent: SDK-first coverage remains canonical here, not a new duplicate epic. Domain promotion items cover query/read (pm-rjqr), lifecycle (pm-98cz), annotations/links (pm-zwpp), schema/config/profile/init (pm-3mna), history maintenance (pm-4a7m), plan workflows (pm-je50), execution/diagnostics (pm-oslr), package/extension lifecycle (pm-x6jf), governance/health (pm-oxrw), docs (pm-ds3b), exemplar CLI (pm-cbwg), and boundary capstone (pm-9x6e). Recommended order: finish typed public primitives before command consolidation flips handlers, then make CLI and MCP pure presentation layers over SDK calls; every primitive needs SDK docs, tests, and behavior parity against existing CLI results."
  "2026-07-07T06:50:47.652Z",maintainer-agent,"Promotion-partition progress reconciled against shipped work (PR #477, commit f7e2ac21): pm-rjqr query/read primitives and pm-98cz item-lifecycle primitives are CLOSED with evidence — PmClient + top-level SDK exports now cover list/get/search/context/next/aggregate/stats and create/update/close/claim/release/copy/delete/restore/focus/start-task/pause-task/close-task, including structured create payloads (pm-395t) and published SDK package-coordinate docs (pm-25d0). Remaining open promotion domains: pm-zwpp annotations/links, pm-je50 plan workflow, pm-4a7m history-stream maintenance, pm-3mna schema/config/profile/init, pm-oxrw governance/health/maintenance, pm-oslr execution/diagnostics, pm-x6jf package/extension lifecycle — then capstone pm-9x6e (zero the 91-entry import-boundary baseline) and exemplar pm-cbwg."
  "2026-07-07T09:44:04.479Z",codex-agent,"Implementation slice update: pm-6abs now contributes to the SDK-first architecture lane by exposing isolated package/extension doctor flags through CLI help, completions, SDK contracts, and MCP/tool schema while keeping extension API method calls safe for package activators that destructure the public API."
  "2026-07-07T21:12:03.550Z",claude-code-agent,"text=Wide PR bundle evidence: implementation spans pm-zwpp annotation/link primitives, pm-3mna customization primitives, pm-oxrw governance primitives, pm-m4iu closed_at metadata correctness, pm-w89s SDK-only integrator story, and this parent SDK-first architecture item. Focused checks passed: pnpm typecheck; node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/sdk/sdk-context-primitives.spec.ts tests/unit/commands/close-command.spec.ts."
