  "2026-07-07T21:48:31.918Z",claude-code-agent,"Verification evidence for wide SDK primitive bundle: pnpm build passed; pnpm typecheck passed; pnpm lint passed (ESLint, jscpd 0 clones, static quality gate); pnpm quality:docs-skills passed; node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage passed with Statements 100%, Branches 100%, Functions 100%, Lines 100%; pnpm changelog:pm:check passed with pm-changelog 2026.7.6 and CHANGELOG.md unchanged; pnpm audit --audit-level high passed with no known vulnerabilities; pm health --check-only --summary --json ok=true; pm validate --check-resolution --check-history-drift --json ok=true with pre-existing resolution metadata warnings only and history_drift ok; installed-package temp proof passed from /tmp/pm-cli-pack-BV1oZ4/unbrained-pm-cli-2026.7.7.tgz in /tmp/pm-sdk-proof-RUtdKV using public @unbrained/pm-cli/sdk imports for lifecycle, comments, append, files, docs, deps, schema, profile, health, and validate."
notes[3]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-05T04:55:45.848Z",maintainer-agent,"Gap analysis 2026-07-05 — src/sdk currently exports extension/package-authoring surfaces only (compose, define, runtime, testing, cli-contracts, profile presets/plan). The PM primitives themselves live in src/core (item, store, search, history, governance, schema, config, session, checkpoint, lock) and src/cli/commands imports them directly; ~60 command modules under src/cli/commands also embed business logic beyond parsing/rendering. Consequence; an SDK-only consumer today cannot create, query, or govern items without shelling out to the CLI."
  "2026-07-05T04:55:46.394Z",maintainer-agent,"Promotion strategy — domain-by-domain (lifecycle, query, annotations, governance, schema/config/profile) with a zero-behavior-change bar per domain; boundary gate (pm-8778) starts as an allowlist ratchet at current import state so it can merge before promotions finish and tighten with each one. Exemplar package (pm-cbwg) is the acceptance proof for the universality story pm-w89s."
  "2026-07-06T08:04:56.740Z",maintainer-agent,"2026-07-06 audit #7: first execution primitive is LIVE — pm-xzhz shipped src/sdk/runtime.ts (PmClient/runAction) with package export ./sdk/runtime, MCP now dispatches through the SDK runner, and the sdk-import-boundary baseline shrank (PR #456, merged 90caa2a7). ADR pm-muhw ACCEPTED (closed 2026-07-05). Remaining promotion partition (rjqr/98cz/zwpp/3mna/oxrw/4a7m/je50/oslr) still covers all 64 live CLI commands; the 18 new dogfood items filed today are presentation-layer (output shape, help, parsing) and do not alter the partition. Note for implementers: runAction gives domain promotions a reference semantics oracle — each narrow primitive (e.g. sdk list/get) must match the equivalent runAction result shape."
